  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC260">
          <l>viḻaiviṉ ṟillai taṉṉiṭat tiyalum.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/162/mode/1up">162</ref>.</p>
      <p>
iccūttiram eṉṉutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, mēl til eṉṉum iṭaiccol mūṉṟaṉporuṭkum uritteṉṟu pōntār; avaṟṟuḷ viḻaiviṉṟillai taṉmai yiṭattiṟkē āvatu.
      </p>
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC260-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘peṟukatil lamma yāṉē’</l>
        <trailer>[kuṟun - 14]</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum.
      </p>
      <p>
eṉavē, maṟṟaiya iraṇṭum ellāviṭattukkum uriya eṉṟavāṟām.    (12)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n213/mode/1up">210</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i – ḷ.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC260-Cena-cit1">
        <l>“appāṉ mūṉṟē tillaiccol”<app><note>col. 253</note></app></l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟu collappaṭṭa mūṉṟaṉuḷ, viḻaiviṉkaṇ varun tillai taṉmaikkaṇallatu vārātu. e–ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
taṉmaikkaṇ varutal mēṟkāṭṭappaṭṭaṉavaṟṟuḷḷum piṟāṇṭuṅkaṇṭukoḷka. iṭam varaiyaṟuttōtāmaiyiṉ, viḻaiviṉṟillai taṉmaikkaṇ varutalum mēlē peṟappaṭṭataṉaip piṉṉuṅ kūṟiṉār, ēṉaiyiṭattu vārāteṉṟu niyamittaṟkeṉpatu.	(12)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/292/mode/1up">292</ref>.</p>
      <p>
itu, muṟkūṟiya til leṉpataṟkup puṟaṉaṭai kūṟukiṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i-ḷ) viḻaiviṉ ṟillai taṉṉiṭattiyalum ―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC260-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>ammūṉ ṟeṉpa tillaic collē</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
yeṉṟa mūṉṟaṉuḷ viḻaiviṉ kaṇ varun tillai taṉmaikka ṇallatu vārā teṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC260-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>‘vārntilaṅku vaiyeyiṟṟuc ciṉmoḻi yarivaiyaip</l>
        <l>peṟukatil lamma yāṉē’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavē, ēṉaiya ellā viṭattiṟku muriya vāyiṉa.    <term xml:lang="en">(12)</term>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n180/mode/1up">173</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ittuṇaiyum palaporuḷ kuṟitta iṭaic col ōti, iṉi oru poruḷ kuṟitta iṭaic col ōtukiṉṟā rākaliṉ,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC260-Tey-cit1">
        <l>mēṟcollap paṭṭavaṟṟuḷ oru coṟkup puṟanaṭai yuṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
i-ḷ: ― viḻaivup poruṭkaṇ varum tillaiccol colluvāṉmāṭṭē nikaḻum. e–ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
utāraṇam mēṟkāṭṭappaṭṭatu.  (12)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
